== 剧情 ==
[[德軍總部：黑曜陰謀|黑曜阴谋]]三年后，纳粹德国发展了先进的科技，从而扭转了失败的局势。1946年7月，美国特种部队{{le|威廉·「B.J」·布拉柯威兹|William "B.J." Blazkowicz}}上校（{{le|布莱恩·布鲁姆|Brian Bloom}}）与飞行员费格斯·里德（Fergus Reid，{{le|吉迪恩·埃默里|Gideon Emery}}）和列兵普罗布斯特·怀亚特三世（Probst Wyatt III，[[A.J.特劳特|A.J.特劳特]]）参加盟军针对“死颅”（Deathshead）威廉·斯特拉塞将军（Wilhelm Strasse，{{le|德怀特·舒尔茨|Dwight Schultz}}）掌控的堡垒和实验室的大规模空袭，三人和其他战友在作战时不慎掉入“死颅”的[[納粹人體實驗|人体实验室]]，随后被捕。“死颅”强迫B.J选择杀掉怀亚特或费格斯，并且临走时开启了实验室的焚化炉<ref name="Chapter 1">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-deathsheads-compound-save-fergus-or-wyatt |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Deathshead's Compound - Save Fergus or Wyatt |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2Clx8Qu?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-deathsheads-compound-save-fergus-or-wyatt |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。随后B.J等人破窗逃生，但B.J被实验室爆炸后产生的碎片击中头部而失憶，成了[[持续性植物状态|植物人]]。后来他被送入波兰的一家精神病院，医院的护士长安雅·奥利瓦（Anya Oliwa，{{le|艾丽卡·巴赫蕾达|Alicja Bachleda}}）负责照顾他。B.J经常看到安雅的父母被迫把病人交给纳粹当局，因为精神疾病，这些病人被纳粹视为{{le|劣等民族|Untermenschen}}<ref name="Chapter 2"/>。

1960年，B.J入院14年后，纳粹德国下令关闭医院，杀死所有病人，安雅的父母也因反抗被杀。此时B.J醒来，杀死了德国人并带安雅逃离<ref name="Chapter 2">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-asylum-kill-commanders-and-save-anya |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Asylum - Kill the Commanders and Save Anya |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2Cp7RjM?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-asylum-kill-commanders-and-save-anya |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。B.J和安雅开车到她的祖父母的农场，在那里他们告诉他，紐約被納粹德國的[[原子彈|原子彈]]轟炸，美國向德國投降，德國及其盟友[[軸心國在第二次世界大戰中的勝利|獲勝]]。德國後來在1949年還背叛和吞併其[[軸心國|軸心國]]盟友[[意大利王國_(1861年–1946年)|意大利帝國]]和[[大日本帝國|大日本帝國]]。1949年10月德國入侵意大利，令意大利和日本結成了同盟對抗德國，同年意大利及其殖民地被佔領，[[日軍|日軍]]和德軍戰鬥至1950年，但日本及其[[大東亞共榮圈|東亞共榮圈]]終究被佔領，德國統一了全世界，抵抗成员也被抓获。這次戰爭被日本及意大利稱為「最後希望之戰」（Last hope war）。 B.J审问了从医院里抓来的官员，得知抵抗成员被监禁在柏林。安雅的爷爷奶奶通过[[什切青|斯德丁]]一个检查站偷运他们到柏林。在火车上，B.J受到了纳粹女军官恩格尔的戏弄，并和安雅确定了他们的恋情<ref name="Chapter 3">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-world-how-choose-right-pictures |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - A New World - How to Choose the Right Pictures |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2CwGFBS?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-world-how-choose-right-pictures |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。到达柏林，安雅帮助B.J进入监狱，营救他14年前幸免于难的战友（怀亚特或费格斯）<ref name="Chapter 4">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-eisenwald-prison-find-key-coal-loader-room |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Eisenwald Prison - Find the Key for the Coal Loader Room |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=20914-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2CzbgFh?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-eisenwald-prison-find-key-coal-loader-room |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。B.J发现抵抗运动是一个复兴的[[克莱稍集团|克莱稍集团]]，由凯洛琳·贝克尔（Caroline Becker，{{le|波尼塔·弗瑞德里希|Bonita Friedericy}}）领导，她的下半身由于受伤而瘫痪<ref name="Chapter 5">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-home-find-project-whisper-folder |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - A New Home - Find the Project Whisper Folder |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2D1ehy7?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-home-find-project-whisper-folder |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

B.J加入后，该组织策划袭击了伦敦的纳粹研究设施，轰炸了他们的行动基地，并窃取了秘密文件和几架私语者直升机<ref name="Chapter 6">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-london-nautica-defeat-giant-robot |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - London Nautica - Defeat the Giant Robot |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-21 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2D3z9Ts?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-london-nautica-defeat-giant-robot |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。文件显示纳粹依靠逆向工程制造了诸如能源武器、电脑AI和超级混凝土等，该技术来源于一个古老的组织“Da'at Yichud”。然而文件也表明有人篡改了超级混凝土的配方，使它容易发霉变质。秘密文件指出Da'at Yichud成员赛特·罗斯（Set Roth，{{le|马克·伊瓦涅|Mark Ivanir}}）与此事有重大联系<ref name="Chapter 7">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-mystery-escape-wolfenstein-castle-easter-egg |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - A Mystery - Escape from Wolfenstein Castle Easter Egg |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-21 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2D69lLI?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-mystery-escape-wolfenstein-castle-easter-egg |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>，而他目前被关押在纳粹的贝利卡集中营里。B.J同意去当卧底，进入集中营见到了赛特，赛特告诉他，纳粹一直使用由他和其他[[犹太人|犹太]]科学家提供的技术生产机器人，并承诺帮助抵抗组织。B.J和赛特控制了机器人，铲除了集中营并解救了囚犯<ref name="Chapter 8">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-camp-belica-how-break-cement-mixer |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Camp Belica - How to Break the Cement Mixer |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-21 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2D7wQ7X?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-camp-belica-how-break-cement-mixer |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

赛特表示纳粹发现了Da'at Yichud的一处藏宝点，其中包括领先当前世界百年的先进科技。赛特标示了其中一个藏宝点的位置，但指出需要[[U型潜艇|U型潜艇]]才能到达<ref name="Chapter 9">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-tactics-find-annes-wedding-ring |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - New Tactics - Find Anne's Wedding Ring |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-22 |accessdate=2014-09-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SY7ltZp2?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-new-tactics-find-annes-wedding-ring |archivedate=2014-09-13 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。后B.J抢夺了一艘U艇，发现它是纳粹潜艇舰队的旗舰，并配有核弹發射器，但其发射代码在纳粹的[[月球殖民|月球基地]]上<ref name="Chapter 11">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-u-boat-access-secret-vault |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - U-Boat - Access the Secret Vault |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-22 |accessdate=2014-09-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SY7xey1T?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-u-boat-access-secret-vault |archivedate=2014-09-13 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>，于是B.J使用在藏宝点获取的扭力球，盗取了一名前往月球的纳粹科学家的身份，渗透到月球基地<ref name="Chapter 13">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-lunar-base-steal-nuclear-keycodes |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Lunar Base - Steal the Nuclear Keycodes |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-23 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2DAI9cf?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-lunar-base-steal-nuclear-keycodes |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。他成功的获得了代码，但返回地球时却发现“死颅”袭击了抵抗组织的基地，并抓捕了一些成员<ref name="Chapter 15">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-under-attack-defend-hideout-and-save-fergus |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order - Under Attack - Defend the Hideout and Save Fergus |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-23 |accessdate=2014-09-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SVD0E6yV?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-under-attack-defend-hideout-and-save-fergus |archivedate=2014-09-11 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

抵抗组织利用扭力球袭击“死颅”的堡垒，营救出了抵抗组织被抓的成员。B.J前往堡垒顶层，在那里再次见到了“死颅”，“死颅”活摘了B.J被俘多年的战友的大脑，并把它放在一个他研製的一台由人腦控制的机器人中。机器人开始攻击B.J，B.J击败了机器人并摧毁了大脑使他的战友得以安息。有些震撼的"死颅"親自駕駛另一台能以閃電作護罩的大型機械人與B.J决斗，B.J擊敗了"死颅"並把他从机械人抽出來凌遲他數刀以為他死去的戰友報仇，但頑圖的“死颅”引爆了手中的手雷試圖和B.J同歸於盡。下半身被手雷炸成重伤但倖存的B.J爬向窗户，目视着安雅撤离囚犯，安雅迟迟未见B.J出现，只好搭乘直升机先行离去。B.J与他的戰友取得联系，告诉他可以发射核武摧毀堡壘<ref name="Chapter 16">{{cite web |url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-return-deathsheads-compound-defeat-deathshead-ending |title=Wolfenstein: The New Order Walkthrough - Return to Deathshead's Compound - Defeat Deathshead - Ending |last=Lavoy |first=Bill |work=[[Prima_Games|Prima Games]] |publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]] |date=2014-05-23 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2DCfc3l?url=http://www.primagames.com/games/wolfenstein-new-order/walkthrough/wolfenstein-new-order-walkthrough-return-deathsheads-compound-defeat-deathshead-ending |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

