《德军总部：新秩序》使用配乐来描绘游戏中的虚构世界，海因斯说：“我们想用具有60年代特色的音乐来区分游戏中不同的音乐，然后经过我们的改编，使它们看起来更加真实。”游戏中总共有八首原创歌曲，另有三首改编自德文歌曲，改编的歌曲不能在游戏中任何地方出现，因为其创作者不希望他们的作品和纳粹联系在一起<ref name="Poly-music">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/3/27/5553192/wolfensteins-bizarre-music-1960s-listen |title=Wolfenstein's bizarre pop music takes a long, strange trip back to the 1960s |last=Good |first=Owen S. |work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=2014-03-27 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2EzQWY4?url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/3/27/5553192/wolfensteins-bizarre-music-1960s-listen |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>{{efn|[[约翰·李·胡克|约翰·李·胡克]]的{{le|Boom Boom (约翰·李·胡克歌曲)|Boom Boom (John Lee Hooker song)|Boom Boom}}，{{le|动物乐队|The Animals}}的{{le|日升之屋|The House of the Rising Sun}}和{{le|Martha and the Vandellas|Martha and the Vandellas}}的{{le|无处可逃 (歌曲)|Nowhere to Run (song)|无处可逃}}改编自德语。<ref name="Poly-music"/>}}。为推动原创歌曲的创作，贝塞斯达成立了唱片公司，为背景故事和一些游戏中虚构的乐队创作歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/04/04/wolfenstein-the-new-order-marketing-team-created-fictional-record-label-for-promo-campaign/ |title=‘Wolfenstein: The New Order’ Marketing Team Created Fictional Record Label For Promo Campaign |last=Danton |first=Eric R. |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |publisher=[[News_Corp|News Corp]] |date=2014-04-04 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2F3FLMf?url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/04/04/wolfenstein-the-new-order-marketing-team-created-fictional-record-label-for-promo-campaign/ |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/05/07/how-developers-created-a-nazi-record-label-for-wolfenstein-the-new-order/ |title=How developers created a Nazi record label for Wolfenstein: The New Order |last=Takahashi |first=Dean |work=GamesBeat |publisher=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]] |date=2014-05-07 |accessdate=2014-05-26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2F6h7Hn?url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/05/07/how-developers-created-a-nazi-record-label-for-wolfenstein-the-new-order/ |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

团队对游戏的音乐给予了高度重视，在游戏开发过程中，作曲家{{le|米克·戈登|Mick Gordon (composer)}}前往瑞典和开发团队会面，与{{le|弗雷德里克·托尔登达尔|Fredrik Thordendal}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/guitarist-from-swedish-metal-band-meshuggah-working-on-wolfenstein-the-new-order/1100-6419582/ |title=Guitarist from Swedish metal band Meshuggah working on Wolfenstein: The New Order |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |date=2014-05-12 |accessdate=2014-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2F9dpCh?url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/guitarist-from-swedish-metal-band-meshuggah-working-on-wolfenstein-the-new-order/1100-6419582/ |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>和{{le|理查德·迪瓦恩|Richard Devine}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=176034 |title=Composer And Sound Designer Richard Devine Switches To Dangerous DAC & Monitor ST Controller |work=Music Industry News Network |publisher=MusicDish |date=2014-07-29 |accessdate=2014-08-09 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2FFwi8m?url=http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=176034 |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=yes |language=en }}</ref>合作指导游戏三天。戈登表示为《新秩序》配乐与其他游戏的不同在于“你签上一个项目，通常他们会给你一个含有150条战斗提示的列表来做”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vgmonline.net/mickgordoninterview/ |title=Mick Gordon Interview: Rebooting Wolfenstein and Killer Instinct |last=Greening |first=Chris |publisher=''Game Music Online'' |date=2014-04-17 |accessdate=2014-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2FIIGOQ?url=http://www.vgmonline.net/mickgordoninterview/ |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

团队在寻找配乐体裁时，最初从[[理查德·瓦格纳|理查德·瓦格纳]]的音乐里寻求灵感，这位作曲家死后受到了纳粹领袖[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]的赞赏。在研究了瓦格纳的作品后，团队发现它们并不符合游戏的基调。随后他们搜索了适合纳粹的音乐风格，最终选择了{{le|失真 (音乐)|Distortion (music)|失真}}的风格。戈登说“有许多模拟失真的类型，各种[[效果器|效果器]]和[[铜管乐器|铜管乐器]]使音乐产生失真的效果”，团队使用[[磁带录音机|磁带录音机]]和{{le|盘式磁带|Reel-to-reel audio tape recording}}等模拟设备从{{le|1960年代音乐|1960s in music|60年代的音乐}}中获取灵感。戈登说配乐是“向[[吉他|吉他]]致敬”，团队中的音乐家们齐心协力，为游戏创作了超过六个小时的配乐<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.capsulecomputers.com.au/2013/11/interview-with-killer-instinct-wolfenstein-the-new-order-composer-mick-gordon/ |title=Interview with Killer Instinct, Wolfenstein: The New Order Composer Mick Gordon |last=Elawar |first=Zac |publisher=''Capsule Computers'' |date=2013-09-15 |accessdate=2014-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2FL2Kf6?url=http://www.capsulecomputers.com.au/2013/11/interview-with-killer-instinct-wolfenstein-the-new-order-composer-mick-gordon/ |archivedate=2014-08-23 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。马蒂斯说：“许多乐谱有奇怪的[[拍号|拍号]]，但它们都非常棒。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://interviewly.com/i/jens-matthies-may-2014-reddit |title=Interviewly - Jens Matthies May 2014 - reddit AMA |last=Matthies |first=Jens |work=[[Reddit|Reddit]] |publisher=Interviewly |date=2014-05-10 |accessdate=2014-06-08 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6S2FNwtRW?url=http://interviewly.com/i/jens-matthies-may-2014-reddit |archivedate=2014年8月23日 |deadurl=yes |language=en |df= }}</ref>

